Name: Date
Description: Date corresponding to TradeTime

Name: LP
Description: Executing LP - counterparty to the trade.

Name: LPStream
Description: Pricing Stream of Executing LP. For example No-Last-look

Name: Symbol
Description: Currency pair. For example EURUSD.

Name: OrderStatus
Description: Status of an order it can be fill "F", reject "R", submitted "S" or cancelled "C"

Name: LiqPool
Description: Pool executing LP belongs to. Typically, liquidity pool is a group of LP aggregated according to some common logic by the end user.

Name: SkewStatus
Description: The underlying skew status of the counterparty, if they are skew safe or not

Name: TradeTimeBucket
Description: TradeTimeBucket - Time buckets every 15 mins (GMT) of the aggregated trades

Name: TradeQuantityUSD
Description: USD Equivalent of TradeQuantity

Name: TradeQuantity
Description: Traded quantity expressed in TradeCurrency

Name: SpreadPnLPM
Description: Spread Paid  in $/million traded

Name: SpreadPnL
Description: Spread Paid in USD

Name: NumEvents
Description: The total number of trades that have taken place
